<LanguageData>
	
	<FertilizerPump.label>肥料泵</FertilizerPump.label>
	<FertilizerPump.description>允许殖民者建造肥料泵，可以用来在任何地方制造可以种植的土地。</FertilizerPump.description>
	
	<GeothermalPower.label>地热能</GeothermalPower.label>
	<GeothermalPower.description>允许殖民者通过在蒸汽泉上建造地热发电机来获得不间断的能源。</GeothermalPower.description>
	
	<Hydroponics.label>水栽培</Hydroponics.label>
	<Hydroponics.description>允许建造水栽培设施来在室内进行快速种植。</Hydroponics.description>
       
	<PneumaticPicks.label>高压气稿</PneumaticPicks.label>
	<PneumaticPicks.description>矿工的稿子效率提高20%。</PneumaticPicks.description>
       
	<Stonecutting.label>岩石切割</Stonecutting.label>
	<Stonecutting.description>允许建造切石桌，可以用来把没用的石头切成有用的石块并可以用于建筑。</Stonecutting.description>
	
	<ElectricSmelting.label>电提炼</ElectricSmelting.label>
	<ElectricSmelting.description>允许建造电提炼器。电提炼器可以用强热和电磁铁把金属块和其他物品中有用的金属提取出来。</ElectricSmelting.description>
	
	<Machining.label>机械化</Machining.label>
	<Machining.description>允许建造把死掉的机器人拆解为有用的金属的机器。</Machining.description>
	
	<NutrientResynthesis.label>营养再合成</NutrientResynthesis.label>
	<NutrientResynthesis.description>营养膏分配机的食物制造消耗降低10%。</NutrientResynthesis.description>
       
	<GunTurretCooling.label>机枪炮塔冷却</GunTurretCooling.label>
	<GunTurretCooling.description>机枪炮塔每次连射发射4颗子弹而不是3颗。</GunTurretCooling.description>
	
	<Mortars.label>迫击炮</Mortars.label>
	<Mortars.description>获得建造可以将炮弹抛过墙壁的迫击炮的能力。</Mortars.description>
	
	<Cremation.label>火化</Cremation.label>
	<Cremation.description>允许建造能把不想要的尸体蒸发的火化炉。</Cremation.description>
	
	<CarpetMaking.label>地毯制作</CarpetMaking.label>
	<CarpetMaking.description>允许殖民者制作地毯来改善环境。</CarpetMaking.description>
	
	<ColoredLights.label>彩色灯</ColoredLights.label>
	<ColoredLights.description>允许殖民者制作装饰性的彩色灯。</ColoredLights.description>
	
	<HospitalBed.label>医疗床</HospitalBed.label>
	<HospitalBed.description>允许殖民者建造可以增加医疗成功率的医疗床。</HospitalBed.description>
	
	<Cryptosleep.label>低温休眠舱</Cryptosleep.label>
	<Cryptosleep.description>允许殖民者建造低温休眠舱，它可以让生物进入生理上"暂停"的状态。</Cryptosleep.description>
	
